Text:
BEEP BEEP... BLUE RIBBON... THANK YOU FOR YOUR
PURCHASE OF OVER 5,000 ZENI, UP TO 10,000 ZENI.
Thanks, Mr. Vendy!
Trick or treat!

BEEP BEEP... RED RIBBON... THANK YOU FOR YOUR
PURCHASE OF OVER 10,000 ZENI.
Th-Thanks...

The newly implemented Mr. Vendy distributes sweets
flawlessly without making any errors.
Delta and Eta are standing a short distance away.
Zzz...
Eta, Eta, wake up! I'm bored!
Zzz... Quiet... *snore*
I wanna do something fun! No sleeping!

...Ha-ruff... I said no sleeping... Don't you hear
me? I'm bored...

Delta finds herself with nothing to do, thanks to
Mr. Vendy's success. Suddenly, she catches wind
of an appetizing scent.
Something smells good... It's coming from over there!

Delta swiftly pivots her body and lunges toward the
source of the scent.
*drool*

Delta reaches an area lined with food stalls.
She comes to a halt in front of a particular
stall and wipes away drool from her mouth.
It looks and smells...delicious... *gulp*
Welcome! Step right up!
What is this?!

It's skewered chicken. This one's seasoned with salt
and grilled. That one's coated with a sweet and spicy
sauce.
*drool*

Judging by your appearance, you're from Mitsugoshi...
Would you like to buy some, young lady?
Can I?!
It'll be 300 Zeni per skewer.
Zeni?!
...I don't have any money...

If you don't have any cash on you, I can put it on
Mitsugoshi's tab.
Mitsugoshi's tab? I can buy it with that?
Yes, ma'am. So what'll it be?

Okay! Gimme the skewered chicken, one of each kind...
No! Five of each kind! Put it on Mitugoshi's tab!
Coming right up!

Delta's eyes sparkle with excitement as she holds
five skewers of chicken in each hand.

This tab thingy...! I don't really get it, but it's
incredible!
As long as I have this...!

Delta sinks her teeth into the skewered chicken.
She devours them quickly before rushing to the
next food stall she spots.

I'd like your limited-edition Halloween quiches!
Hmm...all types! Put it on Mitsugoshi's tab!
Of course. Coming right up!

Pumpkin soup? That's perfect for Halloween! Gimme a
large bowl! Put it on Mitsugoshi's tab!
Sure thing. Enjoy!

No need to slice the pumpkin pie! Just give me a
whole one! Put it on Mitsugoshi's tab!

Ghost pumpkin candles? Hmm... Put it on Mitsugoshi's
tab!
Mitsugoshi's tab!
Mitsugoshi's tab!!!

Delta goes on a shopping spree from stall to stall.
Before she knows it, her hands are full of Halloween
food and trinkets.
What else... Oh right!

I mean, it's Halloween, and there are so many rare
thingies. I'll get souvenirs for Boss man!

Candies, cookies, ghost pumpkin masks...and, and...
Oh! That looks cool as well!

With a radiant smile, Delta enthusiastically resumes
her exploration of the stalls.
